{"word":"βάδην","slug":"βάδην","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βάδην</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βαίνω'><el>βαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>step by step</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>pedetentim</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <i>in marching step</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>β. ταχύ</el> <i>at</i> quick <i>step</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>gradually, more and more</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>walking, marching</i>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> riding, driving, sailing, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}